    "Further, the obtained spectrogram images are used as the input to the AH-CNN-LSTM framework for accurate human motion intention detection.",
    "In this phase, the EEG/EMG signals-based motion intention prediction model is implemented using the AH-CNN-LSTM mechanism.",
    "The adaptive hybridized mechanism is designed based on the integration of CNN and LSTM techniques.",
    "The CNN mechanisms are widely used in the recognition and classification process to offer more accurate disease prediction outcomes than the classical techniques.",
    "Moreover, these CNN techniques perform automated feature extraction and also reduce computation issues."
